Package model

package model
  • Class
    Description
    BuildingCompany
    The BuildingCompany class represents a building company and its operations.
    BuildingCompanyFileSystem
    The BuildingCompanyFileSystem class handles the file system operations for a building company, including creating a report file and updating ongoing and finished project lists in binary files.
    BuildingCompanyModel
    The BuildingCompanyModel interface defines the operations that a building company should support.
    Commercial
    The Commercial class represents a commercial project, extending the Project class.
    FinishedProjectList
    The FinishedProjectList class represents a list of finished projects.
    Industrial
    The Industrial class represents an industrial project, extending the Project class.
    MyDate
    The MyDate class represents a date with day, month, and year information.
    OngoingProjectList
    The OngoingProjectList class represents a list of ongoing projects.
    Project
    The Project class is an abstract class representing a project with common properties.
    ReportList
    The ReportList class represents a list of finished projects with filtering and sorting capabilities.
    Residental
    The Residental class represents a residential project, extending the Project class.
    Road
    The Road class represents a road construction project, extending the Project class.
    Sort
    The Sort class provides methods to sort a list of projects based on different criteria.
    Sort.Order
    Enumeration representing the order of sorting.
    Sort.ProjectType
    Enumeration representing the project type.
    Sort.SortingCategory
    Enumeration representing the sorting category.
